
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Faq";
}
<section class="pb20">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="content-area">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        @*<h2>@ViewBag.Title</h2>*@
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <div class="field-content">
                        <h2><u>FAQs</u></h2>
                        <h3><strong>Is it compulsory to register myself before submitting an admission form online?</strong></h3>
                        <p>Yes, it is compulsory to register with our Online Registration System.</p>
                        <h3><strong>Is Email address compulsory to fill online application form?</strong></h3>
                        <p>Yes, you are required to use E-mail address to register.</p>
                        <h3><strong>If the power/internet connection fails during the application process, what should I do?</strong></h3>
                        <p>Since the data is saved at the end of every stage with the 'Save' button, your data is automatically saved till the previous stage. If you are within a particular stage and the system is interrupted due to power failure or loss of connectivity, then your current stage data will not be saved. Please log in again using your ID and password and complete the form submission process from the stage where the system got interrupted.</p>
                        <h3><strong>What is the detailed process for submission of online application form and action to be taken by the candidate?</strong></h3>
                        <p>The submission of admission form passes through the following stages:</p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Open the URL (<strong>https://ndc.nic.in</strong>)</li>
                            <li>Complete Registration process (After verification you will be intimated with &lsquo;User Name&rsquo; and &lsquo;Password&rsquo; for you).</li>
                            <li>Your &lsquo;User Name&rsquo; and &lsquo;Password&rsquo; is informed through email.</li>
                            <li>Re-login to the system using your &lsquo;User Name&rsquo; and &lsquo;Password.&rsquo; Change password immediately.</li>
                            <li>Read Welcome DO and Handbook for NDC 61.</li>
                            <li>Fill Accomodation Request Form and Participant Registration Form online.</li>
                            <li>Upload your recent passport size Photograph (maximum size 100KB in JPG format).</li>
                            <li>Upload your specimen signature (maximum size 100KB in JPG format).</li>
                            <li>Upload scanned copies of the relevant documents (maximum size 200KB each document in JPG/PDF format).</li>
                            <li>Read the instruction and declaration carefully by clicking the &lsquo;Declaration&rsquo; box.</li>
                            <li>Preview your data and confirm details.</li>
                            <li>Press Next button to see the form preview.</li>
                            <li>After the final submission of online application form, your may download the filled in application form and keep a printout for your record.</li>
                        </ol>
                        <h3><strong>Where do I have to contact after successful submission of form?</strong></h3>
                        <p>Once the application Form is successfully submitted, your form will be scrutinised by NDC staff and after verification you will receive a confirmation to that effect at your registered email address. If a deficiency is found in the application, you will receive a communication from AAQMG informing you about the discrepancy. After successful processing of your form, NDC will provide you further information with regard to confirmation of your accommodation allotment, administrative arrangements,etc in due course of time.</p>
                        <h3><strong>What is the time frame for getting confirmation of my accomodation?</strong></h3>
                        <p>The Accomodation forms submitted through the Online System are scrutinised and confirmed after Board of Officers have convened.</p>

                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

